Paramount Gold Nevada Corp.


            
            Paramount Gold Nevada Corp. engages in the acquisition and exploration of mineral properties. Its projects include sleeper gold, grassy mountain gold, other non-material, and mineral resources. The company was founded on June 15, 1992 and is headquartered in Winnemucca, NV.

            
